/commons/thumb/7/7a/A_Bashi-Bazouk_MET_DT240201.jpg/127px-A_Bashi-Bazouk_MET_DT240201.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7a/A_Bashi-Bazouk_MET_DT240201.jpg/170px-A_Bashi-Bazouk_MET_DT240201.jpg 2x\" data-file-width=\"2633\" data-file-height=\"3722\" /></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">\n<p><i>A Bashi-Bazouk,</i> 1875\n</p>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\" style=\"width: 155px\"><div style=\"width: 155px\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\" style=\"width: 150px;\"><div style=\"margin:15px auto;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Charles_Bargue_%E2%80%93_La_sentinelle_albanaise_en_Caire,_1877.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c5/Charles_Bargue_%E2%80%93_La_sentinelle_albanaise_en_Caire%2C_1877.jpg/88px-Charles_Bargue_%E2%80%93_La_sentinelle_albanaise_en_Caire%2C_1877.jpg\" width=\"88\" height=\"120\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c5/Charles_Bargue_%E2%80%93_La_sentinelle_albanaise_en_Caire%2C_1877.jpg/133px-Charles_Bargue_%E2%80%93_La_sentinelle_albanaise_en_Caire%2C_1877.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c5/Charles_Bargue_%E2%80%93_La_sentinelle_albanaise_en_Caire%2C_1877.jpg/177px-Charles_Bargue_%E2%80%93_La_sentinelle_albanaise_en_Caire%2C_1877.jpg 2x\" data-file-width=\"1130\" data-file-height=\"1532\" /></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">\n<p><i>The Albanian Sentinel in Cairo, 1877</i>\n</p>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Charles_Bargue&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_Orientalist_artists\" title=\"List of Orientalist artists\">List of Orientalist artists</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Orientalism\" title=\"Orientalism\">Orientalism</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Charles_Bargue&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"reflist\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\">Glueck, Grace. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2003/12/26/books/art-review-in-the-days-when-artists-were-taught-how-to-draw.html\">\"In the Days When Artists Were Taught How to Draw\"</a>. <i>The New York Times</i>. The New York Times<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">27 May</span> 2015</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=The+New+York+Times&amp;rft.atitle=In+the+Days+When+Artists+Were+Taught+How+to+Draw&amp;rft.aulast=Glueck&amp;rft.aufirst=Grace&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2003%2F12%2F26%2Fbooks%2Fart-review-in-the-days-when-artists-were-taught-how-to-draw.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACharles+Bargue\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<ul><li>Ackerman, Gerald M., (ed.) &amp; <a href=\"/wiki/Graydon_Parrish\" title=\"Graydon Parrish\">Parrish, Graydon</a>: <i>Charles Bargue avec le concours de Jean-L\u00e9on G\u00e9r\u00f4me: Cours de dessin</i>, French edition, 2003. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/2-86770-165-1\"